{"tid":549643,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"愛情究竟係乜野黎？","createTime":"2018-02-03T21:52:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-04T00:32:46.000Z","uid":145006,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"05afdcc91e292b5844f5cbe13047e2456d4dec16","tid":549643,"uid":145006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-03T21:52:41.000Z","msg":"岩岩同拍左拖四年既女友分開左<br />\n越黎越睇唔透愛情係乜野黎<br />\n<br />\n我係一個九十後男仔，拍左兩次拖<br />\n我想知道究竟點解有咁多人對愛情充滿信心？又點解身邊好多情侶係天作之合又偏偏不歡而散？<br />\n<br />\n好多人覺得只要兩個人真心相愛，冇野係解決唔到，好多人覺得只要你付出，對方會感受到<br />\n<br />\n但我對感情已經冇晒信心，無論結左婚幾多年，甚至有小朋友都會離婚<br />\n亦有好多情侶拍左拖五年，十年，佢地既伴侶地位已經同親人一樣，但最後都分開左<br />\n<br />\n請問你地點解會有信心，勇氣去將自己既心交托比人？"},{"pid":"13ad57a4763eab61cf12b4ec36bf0986314bca85","tid":549643,"uid":2419,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-03T21:55:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-MuPaqGbTspI/T8_ah05kdbI/AAAAAAAABSw/Lof1zQUpt1E/s1600/dog-dragging-chicken.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F2.bp.blogspot.com%2F-MuPaqGbTspI%2FT8_ah05kdbI%2FAAAAAAAABSw%2FLof1zQUpt1E%2Fs1600%2Fdog-dragging-chicken.gif&h=9557a87d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5a20c406306e4996a22c5511708716a3db0f29f6","tid":549643,"uid":145006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"13ad57a4763eab61cf12b4ec36bf0986314bca85","tid":549643,"uid":2419,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-03T21:55:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-MuPaqGbTspI/T8_ah05kdbI/AAAAAAAABSw/Lof1zQUpt1E/s1600/dog-dragging-chicken.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F2.bp.blogspot.com%2F-MuPaqGbTspI%2FT8_ah05kdbI%2FAAAAAAAABSw%2FLof1zQUpt1E%2Fs1600%2Fdog-dragging-chicken.gif&h=9557a87d&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-03T22:30:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  WTF"},{"pid":"dbb9b3ff0754c548cb4e39a84608c1d680d5080a","tid":5